  <name>LikX</name>
  <summary>Screenshot tool with annotation, OCR, and cloud upload</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      LikX is a powerful screenshot utility for Linux that combines capture,
      annotation, OCR text extraction, and cloud upload in one streamlined workflow.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multiple capture modes: fullscreen, region selection, window capture</li>
      <li>Rich annotation tools: pen, highlighter, arrows, shapes, text, blur, pixelate</li>
      <li>OCR text extraction using Tesseract</li>
      <li>Pin screenshots to desktop as floating windows</li>
      <li>Cloud upload to Imgur</li>
      <li>Measurement and numbering tools</li>
      <li>Stamp and callout annotations</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.github.aretedriver.likx.desktop</launchable>

